      γ15n25 κL κLT κLhat κLhatT κT κBT κmid
      (α * γFT) (α * γFB) (α * γST) (α * γSB)
      (by simpa [α] using hFT)
      (by simpa [α] using hFB)
      (by simpa [α] using hST)
      (by simpa [α] using hSB)
